"acronym> requests are interleaved to read or write to multiple disks in "
"parallel. Also, due to the nature of <acronym>RAID</acronym>3, the number of "
"drives must be equal to 3, 5, 9, 17, and so on, or 2^n + 1."
msgstr ""

